The All Blacks' jersey sponsor AIG has launched a powerful new advert, aimed at its Japanese market. They may be the Springboks' arch enemy but they're just so damn difficult to hate.The All Blacks are undoubtedly world rugby's coolest team.And a new advert for insurer AIG will have you marvelling at the tough-tackling prowess of the men from New Zealand.PS: Get ready for a plot twist.